                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17523885" author="emilles" created="Mon, 18 Apr 2022 20:14:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See comment(s) in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-10571&quot; title=&quot;Stub generator misses sibling classes in annotation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-10571&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-10571&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for details on type reference resolution.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17714331" author="emilles" created="Wed, 19 Apr 2023 22:39:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You can add &quot;import some.pack.SomeJavaClass&quot; or write &quot;@SomeAnnotation(SomeJavaClass.class)&quot; to work around the chicken-egg problem that exists with the bi-directional dependencies.  The &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/blob/master/src/main/java/org/codehaus/groovy/tools/javac/JavaAwareCompilationUnit.java&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;JavaAwareCompilationUnit&lt;/a&gt; does know about the java sources being compiled but does not know what classes are declared within.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is an example that relies on an import: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/blob/master/subprojects/groovy-macro/src/main/groovy/org/codehaus/groovy/macro/matcher/internal/MatchingConstraintsBuilder.groovy#L71&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/groovy/blob/master/subprojects/groovy-macro/src/main/groovy/org/codehaus/groovy/macro/matcher/internal/MatchingConstraintsBuilder.groovy#L71&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17714684" author="emilles" created="Thu, 20 Apr 2023 17:12:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/0d11c032af048375dc7ee7ac7dcce5d2e3400f4b&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/0d11c032af048375dc7ee7ac7dcce5d2e3400f4b&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
